title: Mid Wooden Doors to Bottom Mid Flashpoint
description: This is a good Flashpoint for Bottom Mid from Mid Wooden Doors to flash enemies and allow you to swing on them.

title: A Hall Doors to Mid Pillar Flashpoint
description: This is a good Flashpoint for Mid Pillar from A Hall Doors.

title: B Tunnel to Mid Pillar Flashpoint
description: This is a good Flashpoint for Mid Pillar from B Tunnel.

title: Defender Spawn to B Site Aftershock
description: This is a good aftershock to stop someone from planting the bomb. This is also good to kill someone if they don't stop planting the bomb.

title: Post Plant Aftershock For B Site Corner From B Tree
description: Here's a post plant Aftershock setup for the B Site Corner from B Tree.

title: B Site / B Tower Rolling Thunder From B Tree
description: Here's a great Rolling Thunder from B Tree For B Site / B Tower.

title: Support Flashpoint For A Main
description: Here's an early round Flashpoint to support your teammates as they peek into A Main from A Hall.

title: Post Plant Aftershock For Lower A Site From A Main
description: Here's a post plant Aftershock setup for Lower A Site from A Main.

title: B Link / B Canteen Aftershocks For Back B Site Corner
description: Here are two Aftershocks from B Link and B Canteen that can either push players out from behind the back B Site Corner, or deny / delay Spike plant.

title: Early Round A Rope To A Hall Faultine / Flashpoint Combo
description: Here's a great early round setup from Upper A Rope for A Hall to support a teammate's push into A Main and help a teammate take space in A Main.

title: Early Round B Link To B Bench Faultline / Aftershock Combo
description: Here's a great setup from B Link for B Arcade to support a teammate's push into B Arcade / B Bench.

title: Mid Doors Flashpoint
description: A good Flashpoint to push through Mid Doors and take a fight.

title: A Site Entry Rolling Thunder
description: A good Rolling Thunder to execute onto A Site with.

title: A Art to Mid Top Flashpoint
description: A good Flashpoint to push through A Art and peek toward Mid Top.

title: B Ramp to B Club Flashpoint
description: A good Flashpoint to peek the corner of B Ramp into B Club.

title: B Site Flashpoint
description: A good Flashpoint to retake B Site.

title: Aggressive Early Round A Main Flashpoint + Fault Line to Contest Space
description: Use this Flashpoint, and whichever Faultline Variation is the most useful to your team to contest space in A Main.

title: Aggressive Early Round B Main Fault Line
A Site Spike Plant Delay Aftershock
description: Use this A Site Spike Plant Delay Aftershock to force enemy players to either way to plant the spike, or place it in a non-ideal location.

title: Early Round B Main Fault Line to Deny Space
description: Use this early round B Main Fault Line to make it more difficult for the Attackers to take space in B Main.

title: C Site Retake / Site Hold Leer
description: Here's a simple, but effective angle breaking Leer from back C Site for front C Site and C Long.

title: A Site Retake Leer
description: Here's a simple, but effective angle breaking Leer from A Short for back A Site.

title: Early Round Ramen Leer for Top Mid
description: Here's a simple, but effective Leer that can be used to break the angles you are most vulnerable to when peeking Top Mid, creating a short window of time for you and your team to take control of Sight Lines in Mid.

title: B Tower Leer from Mid Mail
description: Here's a simple, but effective Leer that can be used to push through, and / or take control of B Tower from Mid Mail.

title: Early Round Mail Leer for Bottom Mid
description: Here's a simple, but effective Leer that can be used to break the angles you are most vulnerable to when peeking into Bottom Mid, creating a short window of time for you and your team to take control of Sight Lines in Mid. Just be careful of enemy players peeking you from a tight angle on the left side of Bottom Mid.

title: B Tiles to Mid Courtyard Leer
description: This is a good leer to blind anyone peaking B Tiles from Mid or Mid Catwalk. This is perfect to peak an oper peaking you from A Tree.

title: A Main to A Site Leer
description: This is a good leer to blind A Site from A Main allowing your team to execute and take the site.

title: A Lobby to A Main Leer
description: This is a good leer to blind your enemies peaking A Main allowing you to push and take control and clear angles.

title: B Main to B Site Leer
description: This is a good leer to push into B Site and clear angles towards B Switch.

title: B Lobby to B Main Leer
description: This is a good leer to help your team push into B Main from B Lobby.

title: A Rafter to A Site Leer
description: This is a good leer to peak A Rafter with and secure kills on anyone peaking A Site Archway.

title: A Site to A Main Leer
description: This is a good leer to stop an A Main push from A Switch.

title: A Rafter to A Under Leer
description: This is a good leer to blind and peak your enemies hiding in A Under during a retake.

title: A Tree to Mid Catwalk Leer
description: This is a good leer to blind anyone pushing up Mid Catwalk allowing you to get information and back off or peak and get a kill.

title: A Wine to A Main Leer
description: This is a good leer to blind anyone pushing A Main from A Wine allowing you to peak and get a kill or early valuable information.

title: Defender Spawn to B Site Leer
description: This is a good leer to retake B Site with from Defender Spawn.

title: Defender Spawn to Mid Market Leer
description: This is a good leer to blind people pushing up middle or people peaking defender spawn rotation from market.
